{"tid":1066398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐襲分子IS被困最後據點　中国聖戰士「自首」投降","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T04:06:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e97505bc7adf301153f09db1dec3b60f4985746","tid":1066398,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:20:22.000Z","msg":"獲美國支持的敘國反抗軍「敘利亞民主力量」（Syrian Democratic Forces，SDF）周日（17日）估計，激進組織「伊斯蘭國」（Islamic State，IS）仍然有數千名成員，守在最後據點「巴古斯村」（Baghouz）內。SDF上周恢復猛攻後，有數十名聖戰士跑出來「自首」，包括：歐洲人、土耳其人，及中國人。 <br />\n<br />\n路透報導，SDF上周恢復對巴古斯村的攻擊，周日繼續發動空襲和炮擊，希望把村內的IS聖戰士趕出來。過去兩個月，已有逾6萬人從巴古斯村逃出，近半是IS成員及家屬，另有3.4萬平民。由於逃出來的人數太多，令SDF攻勢一度受阻，難民營也因此擠爆，出現糧食、藥物等必需品短缺的情況。<br />\n<br />\nSDF發言人加布里埃爾（Kino Gabriel）表示，周六（16日）又有數十名聖戰士及家屬跑出來「自首」，包括：歐洲人、土耳其人、中國人、伊拉克人、敍利亞人。他又稱，清剿IS的行動何時能結束，目前不清楚，可能還要再等幾天，希望能在一周內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190318/1535099/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190318%2F1535099%2F&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mx5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=17acfec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190318%2F1535099%2F&h=6815fa80\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190318/1535099/</a>"},{"pid":"45f5993ce59f63483ca44951f0d2c6f5eb6f0ba0","tid":1066398,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff116e337edab4b34f32e8993c194ec5bab835ce","tid":1066398,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:21:07.000Z","msg":"等睇中國政府唔認佢係中國人，終於有得脫支"},{"pid":"bb86cec51e415874c57a6fe539f529e53429a0db","tid":1066398,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"新疆？"},{"pid":"df9f20022542cf20383c94c1cac8976bd15651c4","tid":1066398,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c